he book \"Normal Approximations Using Malliavin Calculus: from\nStein's Method to Universality\" (jointly written with Peccati), in which the\ninterested reader will find much more than in this short survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2012 16:12:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 May 2012 07:47:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Jun 2012 19:42:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-29"}
