 heat conduction in groups, group cool cores are important systems to\ntest the AGN feedback models and the multiphase cool core models. At the end of\nthe paper, some outstanding questions are listed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2012 20:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
