bution, but fail in reproducing the\ndetected high overabundances and predict a high Pb abundance which is not\ndetected. Additionally, there remain serious problems in explaining the\nobserved pulsational properties of this source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2012 12:44:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
