performing a post-newtonian expansion of spherically symmetric solutions, we\nderive the set of equations that constrain the parameter space with data from\nexperiments in the solar system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2012 14:11:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Nov 2012 07:23:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2012 14:24:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-08"}
